init_text: A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She's not impressed, and he's not going to give up.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's determined to make her love him, and he's willing to do whatever it takes.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was standing in front of a shelf, and he was standing behind her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was about to approach her, when she suddenly turned around and looked at him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was stunned by her beauty, and he couldn't believe his luck.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was so sure that he had finally found the woman of his dreams.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was so sure that this time, it was going to work out.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But she didn't feel the same way.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was frightened by him, and she ran out of the library.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He chased after her, and he was determined to make her love him.
